    "liveCaveat": "The 2026 World Cup is in progress (June–July 2026). All active-player tournament/career figures (Messi, Mbappé, Ronaldo, Lukaku, Lewandowski — WC goals, caps, international goals, appearances) are changing match-to-match. Such facts are marked \"volatile\": true and should be re-verified after the WC final and the close of the 2025–26 domestic seasons.",
    "fameSystem": "Each fact carries a \"fame\" anchor used to seed question difficulty: 'iconic' = headline record a semi-casual fan could know; 'known' = an engaged fan would know; 'niche' = stats-specialist territory.",
    "difficultySystem": {
      "tiers": ["easy", "intermediate", "hard"],
      "rule": "Difficulty is per-QUESTION, not per-fact, because one fact yields questions of different difficulty. Axis 1 = fact fame (iconic/known/niche). Axis 2 = question form: naming the #1 holder is easiest; naming #2-#3 or a less-famous holder is mid; recalling an exact number, a deep rank (#4+), or an obscure holder is hardest.",
      "easy": "fame=iconic AND form=name-the-#1-holder (or identify the famous record). Intended to be the SMALLEST bucket.",
      "intermediate": "fame=known; OR an iconic fact asked via exact number / 2nd-3rd placing / league-title count.",
      "hard": "fame=niche; OR any deep rank (#4+); OR precise historic numbers; OR obscure single-tournament/match/manager records."
    },
    "conflictsPolicy": "Where the two sources disagree, the primary value is chosen (Wikipedia EUR-at-time for transfer ordering; the most recent / officially-sourced figure for live stats) and the alternative is recorded in \"conflicts\"."
  },

